1800:I flailed my arms around wildly, thinking it'd somehow help me break their grasp.\n;I then opened my mouth wide and bit down on their hand as hard as I could.\p;
1900:〔Yua〕“...Gh!”\p;
2000:But despite that, my attacker remained silent. They weren't even fazed.\p;
2100:I'd bitten down with all my strength, so they must've been in pain... but they still didn't let go.\n;They pressed against me even harder, causing me to lose my balance.\n;No longer able to resist, I fell to the floor with them on top of me.\p;
