2800:Realizing that, the sheer terror sent shivers down my entire body.\n;I struggled as hard as I could, desperately trying to escape.\p;
2900:But under the full weight of her body, I couldn't move an inch. Under normal circumstances, I would've been focused on the fact that our bodies were pressed together, but I lacked the capacity for that right now. Now wasn't the time to be drooling over female contact.\p;
3000:There was only one thing on my mind: I needed to get away somehow, or she'd kill me.\p;
3100:Blood trickled out of Yua's hand where I'd bitten her. Even so, she kept pressing down with all her might, her grip just as intense as when she'd first grabbed hold of me.\p;
3200:She was trying relentlessly to keep my jaw shut, to the point where her nails were digging into my cheeks. A sharp, stabbing pain pierced through my body.\p;
3300:〔Yua〕“Hahh, hahh... It was you... Hahh... Hahh...”\p;
3400:Her mutters came between ragged breaths, much to my horror.\p;
3500:I had to keep resisting, so I grabbed Yua's long hair and pulled hard.\p;
3600:〔Yua〕“Agh...!”\p;
3700:But Yua still didn't budge—all she did was grimace.\n;Using her free hand, she gripped my hand tightly and dug in her nails once again.\p;
3800:〔Takumi〕“MMMPH...!”\p;
3900:The immense pain forced me to let go. And then, using that tiny opening, she pinned my hands to the floor.\p;
4000:〔Yua〕“Hahh, hahh... It was you... wasn't it? It was you...!”\p;
